Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Dialogue
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.99,0:00:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,任務 一對一戰鬥模式
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.30,0:00:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,發起全力進攻
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.02,0:00:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,戰場 月對月
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.47,0:00:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,對方玩家 理央北條
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.47,0:00:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,戰鬥開始
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.79,0:00:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,接得不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.48,0:01:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,看來處理手段有長進 理央
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.38,0:01:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,這是今天第26回對戰
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.91,0:01:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,這次我就贏下了 師父
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.52,0:01:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,儘管來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.35,0:01:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,下盤也適應了模擬環境
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.63,0:01:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,斬擊也挺凌厲
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.99,0:01:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,所謂士別三日刮目相看
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.31,0:01:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,說得挺對
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.33,0:01:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,就是現在
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.30,0:01:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,明明瞄準了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.92,0:01:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,持炮不穩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.13,0:01:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,這方面還得再努力
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.11,0:02:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,人類自從潛入宏大的網路已經半世紀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.97,0:02:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,網路改變了人們的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.32,0:02:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,也改變了現實與虛擬的邊界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.12,0:02:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,其中當然少不了鋼彈
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.10,0:02:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,結交朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.92,0:02:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,創造作品
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.21,0:02:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,購買鋼普拉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.14,0:02:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,交流拼裝技術
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.26,0:02:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,分享作品
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.63,0:02:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,還有
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.82,0:02:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,名為鋼普拉對戰的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.68,0:02:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,全新社交模式
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.53,0:02:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,這個以鋼彈和鋼普拉為主題的虛擬世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.93,0:02:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,名為鋼彈元宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.98,0:04:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,早安 理央
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.47,0:04:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,今天也去老師那裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.80,0:04:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.91,0:04:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,帶上這個
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.11,0:04:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.52,0:04:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,代我向老師問好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.41,0:04:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,好 我出門了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.43,0:04:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我出發了 核
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.38,0:05:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,喲理央 早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.14,0:05:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.73,0:05:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,要出門嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.09,0:05:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 去購物中心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.21,0:05:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.31,0:05:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.91,0:05:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,理央
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.56,0:05:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,今天浪不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.41,0:05:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,一起衝浪嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.79,0:05:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 今天要去別的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.69,0:05:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,別的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.68,0:05:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,就是那個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.94,0:05:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,鋼普拉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.74,0:05:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,對 就是這
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.92,0:05:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,他最近好像挺迷這個
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.23,0:05:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.04,0:05:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,喲理央
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.73,0:05:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,傑夫叔 阿嘍哈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.95,0:05:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,賽麗亞在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.36,0:05:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 在老地方
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.00,0:05:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,好像還在睡呢 能幫我叫醒她嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.45,0:05:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,好的 知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.94,0:05:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,早安 賽麗亞
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.77,0:06:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,沁人心脾
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.27,0:06:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,又熬夜了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.07,0:06:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,又從頭看了一遍鋼彈ZZ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.98,0:06:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,一眨眼就到早上了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.03,0:06:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,話說你和鋼普拉師父的對戰怎樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.32,0:06:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 她叫面具女士
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.42,0:06:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,表現比之前好多了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.54,0:06:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,還是輸了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.71,0:06:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,看看錄像吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.28,0:06:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.51,0:06:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,下盤更穩了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.93,0:06:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,改良得挺合適
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.83,0:06:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 但是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.56,0:06:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,之前改了肩部的可動區域吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.92,0:06:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,恐怕是受其影響
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.49,0:06:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,系統判定穩定不住重火器的後坐力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.76,0:06:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,該怎麼改呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.49,0:06:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,方案很多
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.15,0:06:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,肩部改成二重關節
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.47,0:06:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,或者換新關節
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.30,0:07:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,拿我的樣機做參考吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.12,0:07:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.47,0:07:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,明天你說要在家登入元宇宙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.77,0:07:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 套件送到家 已經裝好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.49,0:07:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,要趕在之前完工啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.98,0:07:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.30,0:07:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,這次改裝重點是加工精度
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.28,0:07:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,精度
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.58,0:07:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,粗糙的加工無法發揮部件的性能
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.62,0:07:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,好難懂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.37,0:07:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,現在的理央可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.12,0:07:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.48,0:07:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.36,0:07:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.93,0:07:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,失敗也沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.09,0:07:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,從頭再來的機會多的是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.72,0:07:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,最重要的是享受過程
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.49,0:07:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,以自己想像的藍圖
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.45,0:08:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,構建出理想的形態
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.17,0:08:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,並以此為目標努力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.70,0:08:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,從不斷的試錯中
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.69,0:08:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,增長經驗和知識
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.85,0:08:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.69,0:08:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,做得漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.57,0:08:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,理央
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.82,0:08:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.02,0:08:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,好嘞
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.66,0:08:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,賽麗亞 有勞你關門了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.89,0:08:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.14,0:08:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,理央 再見
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.48,0:08:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,再見 傑夫叔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.96,0:08:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,但是真可惜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.78,0:08:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,賽麗亞沒法一起來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.57,0:08:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.28,0:08:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,想介紹給面具女士認識一下呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.56,0:08:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,駕駛著這個鋼普拉介紹我拼裝模型的師父
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.73,0:09:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,得了吧 我挺害羞的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.33,0:09:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,別糾結了 快回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.90,0:09:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,還要準備吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.76,0:09:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.73,0:09:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,那晚安 賽麗亞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.55,0:09:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,晚安 理央
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.23,0:09:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.16,0:09:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.99,0:09:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,對了 得告訴師父我甚麼時候登錄
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.55,0:09:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,邀請面具女士
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.72,0:10:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,喲 理央
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.98,0:10:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,感謝邀請
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.58,0:10:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,師父
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.76,0:10:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,歡迎來到我的模型房間
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.74,0:10:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,這邊請
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.25,0:10:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,看吧 師父
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.43,0:10:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,這是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.20,0:10:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.59,0:10:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,這是我的鋼普拉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.18,0:10:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,燦陽鋼彈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.63,0:10:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,換了肩部關節吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.11,0:10:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.02,0:10:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我的模型師父指導我改的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.11,0:10:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,這是完成品嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.47,0:10:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,不好說
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.56,0:10:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,說不定還能改進
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.65,0:10:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,但失敗了從頭再來就好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.15,0:10:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,試錯很重要
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.08,0:10:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.57,0:10:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,正是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.79,0:10:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,燦陽鋼彈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.75,0:11:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,好名字
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.56,0:11:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,歡迎來到SIDE-G
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.08,0:11:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我是鋼彈元宇宙的AI梅洛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.11,0:11:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡可以體驗各種活動
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.24,0:11:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,敬請享受鋼彈元宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.85,0:11:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,走主路嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.59,0:11:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我還以為直接去競技場呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.09,0:11:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,現在大會堂有live嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.91,0:11:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,不是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.39,0:11:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.53,0:11:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我想看到是那個
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.64,0:11:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,川口名人製作的驚異鋼彈巴巴託斯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.46,0:11:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,說起來是今天來著
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.00,0:11:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我去看看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.34,0:11:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,好厲害 太酷啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.70,0:11:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,近距離能看出細節處理得相當棒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.60,0:12:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,但可不只是纖細
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.66,0:12:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,戰鬥也一定很強
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.52,0:12:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,這鋼彈可以稱為傑作
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.01,0:12:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,咦 好久不見
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.32,0:12:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,文奈啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.67,0:12:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,最近怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.26,0:12:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,挺好 你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.77,0:12:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,還是老樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.23,0:12:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.89,0:12:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,本想多聊聊 但我還有事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.10,0:12:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.95,0:12:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,之後再聯繫
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.03,0:12:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,理央
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.81,0:12:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,怎樣 心滿意足了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.71,0:12:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 非常滿足
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.28,0:12:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,接下來該模型對戰了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.18,0:12:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,想一對一自由對戰的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.67,0:12:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,進入後系統就自動匹配旗鼓相當的對手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.16,0:12:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,好不容易來一次想試試團體戰
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.55,0:12:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.18,0:12:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.27,0:13:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,今天沒帶鋼普拉登錄
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.06,0:13:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,不是這個意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.04,0:13:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,不會再有勞你的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.01,0:13:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我也想學著獨立
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.09,0:13:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,意識不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.44,0:13:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,但是怎麼開始呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.64,0:13:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,團體戰招募隊友的很多
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.90,0:13:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,看著不錯可以加入
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.88,0:13:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,申請通過後 會被邀請到隊伍房間
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.79,0:13:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,這個看起來不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.47,0:13:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,就這個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.67,0:13:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,好快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.99,0:13:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,申請通過了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.46,0:13:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.88,0:13:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,喲 初次見面
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.25,0:13:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,歡迎加入
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.83,0:13:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.77,0:13:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我是陸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.64,0:13:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.91,0:13:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你好 我是理央
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.39,0:13:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,莎拉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.51,0:13:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.86,0:13:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,這是創形者的陸和莎拉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.33,0:13:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,有人憧憬有名的玩家
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.54,0:13:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,就用同樣的形象和網名
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.43,0:13:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.61,0:13:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.61,0:13:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我們是募集一位成員
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.34,0:13:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,不用擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.01,0:14:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我是陪這孩子來的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.08,0:14:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.69,0:14:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我們想進行隊內二對二戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.71,0:14:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,但是幸夫
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.64,0:14:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我朋友突然來不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.34,0:14:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,陸 桃香和菖蒲在等著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.78,0:14:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.38,0:14:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,那就快去戰場吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.25,0:14:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.17,0:14:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,準備好了嗎 理央
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.29,0:14:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.11,0:14:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,理央北條
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.00,0:14:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,燦陽鋼彈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.69,0:14:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.80,0:14:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,理央 來這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.96,0:14:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,陸的模型超帥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.16,0:14:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,00鋼彈的改版
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.71,0:15:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,完成度好高
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.41,0:15:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.70,0:15:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,這名為弧光型00鋼彈潛行者
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.62,0:15:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,理央的模型也挺帥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.85,0:15:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,非常漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.24,0:15:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.14,0:15:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,名叫燦陽鋼彈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.92,0:15:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,陸 趕緊的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.37,0:15:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.77,0:15:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,那是甚麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.33,0:15:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,忍者型的SD鋼彈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.57,0:15:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,厲害 還有這種路線
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.43,0:15:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,這個卡普爾做得也非常精巧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.61,0:15:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,一眼就能看出水平在我之上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.82,0:15:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,然後這位是參加對戰的理央
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.90,0:15:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我是桃 多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.99,0:15:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,菖蒲 這機體是F9之1改
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.26,0:15:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我是理央
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.10,0:15:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,請多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.40,0:15:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,這次的戰場是隕石帶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.22,0:15:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,要一邊注意障礙物
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.14,0:15:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,一邊注意互相的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.64,0:15:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,還有敵人的位置 加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.96,0:15:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.49,0:15:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,不用緊張
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.56,0:15:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,盡情享受鋼普拉對戰吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.85,0:15:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.19,0:15:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.12,0:16:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,對戰開始
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.41,0:16:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我可不會放水
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.72,0:16:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,當然
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.73,0:16:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,被壓制了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.11,0:16:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,休想逃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.03,0:16:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,陸他們真厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.37,0:16:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,來囉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.74,0:16:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,理央
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.05,0:16:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事 我可以
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.18,0:16:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,團體戰和一對一果然不同
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.84,0:16:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,隨著情報量增加 要考慮的東西也變多了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.83,0:16:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,但正是這樣才有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.20,0:16:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,不愧是聲名遠揚的創形者
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.32,0:16:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,這對理央來說也是不錯的一課吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.02,0:16:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,面具女士
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.40,0:17:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,不 很開心能見到你迴歸模型對戰
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.00,0:17:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,對理央保密哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.65,0:17:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我很害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.58,0:17:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,那我們敘敘舊如何
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.29,0:17:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,名人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.75,0:17:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,這次再會
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.67,0:17:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,必然有其意義
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.75,0:17:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,無論對我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.63,0:17:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,還是對你們
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.05,0:17:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,真行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.15,0:17:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.30,0:17:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,天地咆哮掌
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.82,0:17:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,贏了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.69,0:18:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,桃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.59,0:18:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Trans-Am
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.38,0:18:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉了 菖蒲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.37,0:18:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.02,0:18:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,一換一嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.05,0:18:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,到賽點了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.89,0:18:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,對現在的理央來說是不是負擔太重了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.52,0:18:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,別以為只有Trans-Am能提高機體性能
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.15,0:18:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,菖蒲忍法
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.81,0:18:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,擾亂之術
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.69,0:18:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,這便是我的必殺技
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.08,0:19:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,所有的攻擊都有傷害
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.80,0:19:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,是有質量的殘像嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.59,0:19:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我甚麼都做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.11,0:19:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,甚至不能支援陸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.92,0:19:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,那是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.68,0:19:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我還
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.49,0:19:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,可以
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.85,0:19:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣下去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.39,0:19:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,竟不理會我的子機
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.31,0:19:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,但也在預料之內
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.94,0:19:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,勝利我收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.10,0:19:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,贏的是我們
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.66,0:20:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,勝者 陸與理央
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.67,0:20:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,贏了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.22,0:20:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯 我們贏了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.59,0:20:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝你 理央
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.64,0:20:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,贏了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.61,0:20:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,贏了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.85,0:20:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,哎 輸了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.15,0:20:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.27,0:20:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,真是不容大意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.73,0:20:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,要回去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.27,0:20:36.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我好歹也知道自己甚麼立場
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.07,0:20:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,有朝一日再會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.36,0:20:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.17,0:20:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.72,0:20:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,今天好開心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.69,0:20:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我也是 今天非常盡興
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.39,0:20:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,下次再玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.70,0:20:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,可別忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.00,0:20:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 當然
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.22,0:20:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,下次不會輸了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.74,0:20:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我也不會輸的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.17,0:20:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我才是不會輸的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.59,0:21:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,再會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.64,0:21:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 再會
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.97,0:21:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,盡興了嗎 理央
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.83,0:21:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 非常盡興
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.34,0:21:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,先發消息感謝陸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.90,0:21:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.01,0:21:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然和那個陸加了好友
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.08,0:21:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,這是認證標誌？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.04,0:21:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.82,0:21:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,那個陸是真的創形者
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.03,0:21:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,很厲害吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.51,0:21:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,師父知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.25,0:21:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.42,0:23:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,師父
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.01,0:23:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,明白了嗎 人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.94,0:23:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,人類看到自己便會不爽
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.50,0:23:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,所以要摧毀
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.66,0:23:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,無論多少次
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.28,0:23:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,無論多少次
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.90,0:23:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,師父
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.21,0:23:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,再也別來這個世界了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.94,0:23:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.34,0:23:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,賽麗亞
